# Mobile agent scope

## Owns

- `apps/mobile/` only

## Design tokens

- Use `apps/mobile/src/theme.ts` (`colors`, `radius`, `shadows`, `space`).
- Use `withAppFont()` from `src/lib/typography.ts`.
- No inline hex when a token exists.

## Campaign UI

- Active promo: `campaign.applies_now === true` (not carousel `featured` index).
- Card detail `promotion` is venue-wide; sticker only when API returns promotion.

## Safe area

- `headerIncludesSafeArea` only for screens that need it (e.g. notifications) — not all tab screens.

## Verify

```bash
cd apps/mobile && npm run typecheck
```

## Must not

- Change Laravel API without backend spec in task yaml.
- Version bump / TestFlight (Release agent).
